# shadcn UI Usage Guidelines

This project uses **shadcn UI** for all UI elements. shadcn UI is already initialized and configured with the following settings:

- **Style**: new-york
- **RSC**: React Server Components enabled
- **Base Color**: neutral
- **Icon Library**: lucide
- **CSS Variables**: enabled

## Configuration Files

- Main config: [components.json](mdc:components.json)
- Global styles: [src/app/globals.css](mdc:src/app/globals.css)
- Utilities: [src/lib/utils.ts](mdc:src/lib/utils.ts)

## Component Aliases

```
@/components/ui -> src/components/ui/
@/components -> src/components/
@/lib/utils -> src/lib/utils
@/hooks -> src/hooks/
@/lib -> src/lib/
```

## Installation Commands

If shadcn UI needs to be initialized (should already be done):
```bash
npx shadcn@latest init
```

To add new components (example for button):
```bash
npx shadcn@latest add button
```

